*  FUNCTION = This is a front-end terminal map                        *
*             used by the FEPI sample programs.                       *
*                                                                     *
*---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*                                                                     *
* CHANGE ACTIVITY :                                                   *
*                                                                     *
*     $MOD(DFH0MZ2),COMP(FEPI),PROD(CICS TS ):                        *
*                                                                     *
*     PN= REASON REL YYMMDD HDXIII : REMARKS                          *
*    $P0= M30650 530 981113 HD4OGB  : Fix copyright statements        *
